## Why a separate license for docs

The Constitution and vault are the architectural thinking that
makes RAPP coherent — the *digital organism* framing, the rappid
lineage protocol, the kernel-as-DNA discipline, the additive-only
chat envelope, the species-archive pattern. Code can be reproduced
in a weekend by anyone who reads it; this thinking is the platform's
distinctive substance.

CC BY-NC 4.0 lets the thinking travel — quoted in talks, papers,
blog posts, classrooms — while preventing wholesale repackaging as
a competitor's proprietary documentation.

